    "description": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"ancestral-archery\">Ancestral Archery</h3><p>Throughout the ages the Koyumi clan have trained their young to use bows from the moment they were strong enough to hold one. Their connection to their family is so great they were able to channel the experience and knowledge of those who have passed into the world for a brief moment, to continue their hunt once more.</p><h4 id=\"koyumi-traits\">Koyumi Traits</h4><p><strong>Ability Score Increase:</strong> +2 Dex or Str, +1 Wis<br /><strong>Speed:</strong> Your base walking speed is 30 feet<br /><strong>Skill Proficiencies:</strong> Martial Arts, Perception<br /><strong>Weapon Proficiencies:</strong> You are proficient with all Bows</p>",
